data.description: East Marion, North Fork - Pebble Beach Farms Soundfront BEACH community located at 280 The Short Lane, East Marion. You will easily see why the builder's of this substantial residence call it: Casa degli Sogno - the house of dreams! Southern estate vibe with North Fork provenance. Elevator entry to main floor living space that features open floor plan and contemporary living with vaulted ceilings. Large living room is highlighted by gas fireplace and terrace access. Dining room and kitchen are designed for entertaining....large pantry and laundry room. Substantial owner's suite w/terrace access, large walk in closets and supersized en suite bath (shower, walk in tub, dual vanities, commode and storage). Office/den/Bedroom and full bath - plus walk-up attic with skylights and dormers to let the light in! multiple car garage, plus apartment with full bath outfitted as a private suite. Large level lot with room for pool (expired pool permit on file) in premier beach community that offers private Sound beach, tennis and more! All moments to the vibrant village of Greenport and other North Fork amenities including farmstands, shopping, wineries and farm to table restaurants.
